          <title>Trump picks Project 2025 author Russell Vought to lead budget office</title>
          <description><![CDATA[President-elect Donald Trump tapped Project 2025 co-author Russell Vought to serve as the director of the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) during his second administration. Vought served as Trump's OMB deputy director during his first term in the Oval Office.]]></description>
